TY  - JOUR
TI  - Multivariate Regression and Simultaneous Equation Models when the Dependent Variables Are Truncated Normal
AU  - Amemiya, Takeshi
AB  - [This paper extends the single equation regression model with the truncated dependent variable considered by Tobin [10] and Amemiya [1] to multivariate and simultaneous equation models and proposes a computationally simple consistent estimator.]
